# ProtoERP вЂ” Employee & Finance Management System
## Implementation Plan (FINAL)

> **Stack**: Go В· React Native В· PostgreSQL В· Docker  
> **Pattern**: Clean Architecture + Hexagonal + DDD (Pragmatic) + semi-CQRS  
> **Mode**: Multi-Tenant В· Mobile-first (React Native + Emulator)

---

## Architecture Decision Records (ADR)

| Keputusan | Pilihan | Alasan |
|---|---|---|
| Frontend | React Native (Expo) | Native mobile, emulator-ready |
| Multi-tenant | `tenant_id` column + Row-Level Security | Simpel, scalable, tidak perlu DB per tenant |
| Finance scope sekarang | Payroll + Reimbursement + Budget | MVP dulu |
| Finance scope masa depan | Full GL (double-entry), AP, AR | Dipreparasi via COA + Journal table dari awal |
| HTTP Router | `chi` atau `echo` | Lightweight, idiomatic Go |
| ORM / Query | `sqlx` + raw SQL | Tidak pakai ORM di domain, sesuai prinsip |
| Migration | `golang-migrate` | Battle-tested, supports PostgreSQL |
| Validation | `go-playground/validator` | Standard di Go ecosystem |
| JWT | `golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | Standard JWT |

---

## Multi-Tenant Design

Setiap tabel utama memiliki `tenant_id UUID NOT NULL` yang di-inject via middleware setelah JWT decode.

```
Request в†’ JWT Middleware (extract tenant_id + user_id) в†’ Context в†’ UseCase в†’ Repository (filter by tenant_id)
```

```sql
-- Contoh: tabel employees
CREATE TABLE employees (
    id          UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    tenant_id   UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES tenants(id),
    nik         VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    full_name   VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    ...
    UNIQUE(tenant_id, nik)
);
```

---

## GL/AP/AR Extensibility (Dipersiapkan dari Awal)

Tabel `chart_of_accounts` (COA), `journal_entries`, dan `journal_lines` dibuat dari **Phase 1** meski belum dipakai UI.  
Payroll dan Reimbursement akan auto-post ke journal saat Phase 4+.

```
Payroll Generated в†’ journal_entries (debit: Beban Gaji, kredit: Hutang Gaji)
Reimbursement Approved в†’ journal_entries (debit: Beban, kredit: Kas/Bank)
```

